Class Document

java.lang.Object
  Document

public class Document
extends java.lang.Object

A document has an id and a "tag". This "tag" represents what the document is all about (for a music file, it could represent its genre), but it is not known to the user until he/she gets to "evaluate" (e.g., download, read) it.
